# TypeScript Rules

Strict mode ON — `noUncheckedIndexedAccess`, `exactOptionalPropertyTypes`.

## Domain Types

```ts
type TransactionType = "income" | "expense"
type TransactionId = string & { readonly brand: "TransactionId" }

interface Transaction {
  id: TransactionId
  type: TransactionType
  amount: number
  category: string
  description: string
  date: Date
}

// ✅ Props eksplisit
interface MessageBubbleProps {
  role: "user" | "assistant"
  content: string
  className?: string
}

// ✅ unknown + validate, bukan any — terutama output AI
function parseAiTransaction(raw: unknown): Transaction { ... }
```

## Naming
- Components → PascalCase file · Hooks → `useXxx.ts` · Utils → camelCase
- Constants → `SCREAMING_SNAKE` · Types → PascalCase

## Validasi & Forms
- Zod schema di `lib/validations/` — validasi input user & response AI
- React Hook Form + Zod untuk form manual (jika ada)
- Server state → TanStack Query, bukan Zustand
- Amount & currency logic di `lib/finance/` — bukan scattered di component
